---
title: Harira-Style Chicken Breast Tenders, Lentil and Veggie Stew with Feta and Toasted Flatbread Wedges
description: Inspired by the traditional Moroccan soup harira, tonight's recipe combines lentils, Moroccan spices, chicken tenders, sweet zucchini and savoury crushed tomatoes for a comforting bowl of goodness. Make sure you sop up every last bit with the flatbread wedges!
